  "lines": [
    {
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "start": 3901,
      "label": "fluff",
      "line_number": 1794
    },
    {
      "text": "been doing a lot of drugs and dwelling on my traumas.",
      "start": 3903,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 1795
    },
    {
      "text": "And mushrooms showed me that my biggest trauma",
      "start": 3909,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 1796
    },
    {
      "text": "was learning that Santa Claus was not real.",
      "start": 3913,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 1797
    },
    {
      "text": "But here's the thing.",
      "start": 3917,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 1798
    },
    {
      "text": "When you think about Santa, when you're on mushrooms,",
      "start": 3918,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 1799
    },
    {
      "text": "you realize they've been talking about Santa",
      "start": 3921,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 1800
    },
    {
      "text": "for thousands of years.",
      "start": 3923,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 1801
    },
    {
      "text": "And they're going to keep talking about Santa",
      "start": 3926,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 1802
    },
    {
      "text": "for thousands of years.",
      "start": 3929,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 1803
    },
    {
      "text": "Yet I'm only going to live for like 80 years.",
      "start": 3930,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 1804
    },
    {
      "text": "So in a way, isn't Santa more real than me?",
      "start": 3932,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 1805
    },
    {
      "text": "So here's my question.",
      "start": 3942,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 1806
    },
    {
      "text": "If Santa's not real, and I'm less real than Santa,",
      "start": 3945,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 1807
    },
    {
      "text": "then why did it feel real when he molested me at the mall?",
      "start": 3951,
      "label": "punchline",
      "line_number": 1808
    },
    {
      "text": "Our traumas ground us in the physical reality.",
      "start": 3959,
      "label": "tag",
      "line_number": 1810
    },
    {
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "start": 3964,
      "label": "fluff",
      "line_number": 1812
    }
  ]
